00:30:45,534 --> 00:30:48,097
- He has it. Just look for his ID.
- Come on!

522
00:30:48,097 --> 00:30:49,479
You're the one who did wrong here.

523
00:30:49,479 --> 00:30:51,923
- Look for his ID!
- Calm down, Sir.

524
00:30:51,923 --> 00:30:54,525
- What's wrong with you, you punk?
- What?

525
00:30:54,525 --> 00:30:56,476
- Get over here!
- Calm down!

526
00:30:56,476 --> 00:30:58,667
- What's going on?
- Look through his pockets!

527
00:30:58,667 --> 00:31:00,499
- It's got to be in there!
- Stop it!

528
00:31:00,499 --> 00:31:02,642
You just have to search his pockets for it!

529
00:31:02,642 --> 00:31:04,475
- If you search him, you'll find it!
- Come on!

530
00:31:04,475 --> 00:31:06,766
- Does he want to get beaten up?
- It must be a fake ID!

531
00:31:06,766 --> 00:31:08,239
- You can find it in his pockets!
- Calm down!

532
00:31:08,239 --> 00:31:10,751
What do you mean they're minors?

533
00:31:10,751 --> 00:31:12,753
- Dad!
