Three Months Before

536
00:31:40,660 --> 00:31:42,482
Hey!

537
00:31:54,353 --> 00:31:56,665
Why are you over there?

538
00:31:56,665 --> 00:31:59,789
I work over there starting today.

539
00:31:59,789 --> 00:32:02,481
A guy I know introduced me to one of his friends.

540
00:32:02,481 --> 00:32:05,060
So I'm a store manager now.

541
00:32:05,713 --> 00:32:09,199
I went to the Middle East and even rode boats.

542
00:32:09,199 --> 00:32:11,680
I worked hard all these years

543
00:32:11,680 --> 00:32:13,753
to pay off all of my debts.

544
00:32:13,753 --> 00:32:15,105
Now,

545
00:32:15,105 --> 00:32:19,999
I want to live close by you and my kids.

546
00:32:19,999 --> 00:32:21,890
I can't believe you.

547
00:32:21,890 --> 00:32:24,304
You disappeared while they were growing up.

548
00:32:24,304 --> 00:32:26,195
Now, you suddenly want to show up?

549
00:32:26,195 --> 00:32:27,678
I didn't contact you

550
00:32:27,678 --> 00:32:31,260
because I wanted to make sure you didn't get hurt.

551
00:32:31,260 --> 00:32:34,974
Now that I'm close by,

552
00:32:34,974 --> 00:32:37,037
- you'll be all right.
- Forget it.

553
00:32:37,037 --> 00:32:40,910
We're doing just fine without you. So don't act like you know us!

554
00:32:41,569 --> 00:32:43,573
I can't believe this.
